snippet.title: E3 2002 - Presentation RESIDENT EVIL ONLINE ("Outbreak")
snippet.description:
Straight from Sony's archives, the first public presentation of RE Online (before it was renamed "Outbreak") during E3 2002, by Kazuo Hirai.
High quality.
